Zeus must be: it took four years with not just one programmer but TWO!  Its
the most advanced BBS system on any platform (probably) and is, of course,
the only choice if you want to run a ZAPP server.

   The Zeus BBS demo should be available on the Aminet, from our support
sites or any good BBS near you!

